ode_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "emailservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-2", "cartservice-1", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["cartservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "adservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "frontend-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-18T19:10:04Z to 2025-06-18T19:29:04Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-18 19:10:04+00:00 to 2025-06-18 19:29:04+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "emailservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-2", "cartservice-1", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["cartservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "adservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "frontend-2"]}, "metric_analysis_findings": "对分析时段内的异常指标进行综合汇总。在 `anomaly_metrics` 数据中，有多个服务、组件出现异常。以下是初步发现：\n\n### 异常指标Key:\n\n- `client_error_ratio`\n- `error_ratio`\n- `rrt`\n- `store_unhealth_count`\n- `duration_99th`\n\n### 异常组件和原因分析:\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"store_unhealth_count\", \"duration_99th\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend组件出现错误率明显升高，例如 server_error_ratio的P99从正常时的0.0暴增至28.57，关联到可能的依赖服务故障。\",\n      \"evidence\": {\n        \"metric\": \"error_ratio\",\n        \"normal_p99\": 0.0,\n        \"fault_p99\": 35.28,\n        \"change_ratio\": 2.0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"component-mapping=By Pod.", "trace_analysis_findings": "我已经成功获取了包含异常调用链的追踪数据，接下来是对数据的全面扫描以找出所有显著的异常调用链，并根据数据特征识别延迟瓶颈和错误传播路径。\n\n### 异常调用链扫描结果\n\n#### 延迟分析\n以下是通过异常数据计算得出的延迟倍数：\n\n- **ProductCatalogService/GetProduct**\n  - Frontend to ProductCatalogService: 延迟倍数 = 3955.26 / 1148.03 ≈ 3.44 (请求发生频次: 38)\n  - Frontend to ProductCatalogService: 延迟倍数 = 3930.89 / 1137.18 ≈ 3.46 (请求发生频次: 37)\n\n#### 错误传播路径\n- **Region is unavailable**\n  - Frontend和ProductCatalogService之间的错误状态码为\"Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\" (请求发生频次: 93)\n  - CheckoutService到ProductCatalogService的调用也显示错误\"Region is unavailable\"（请求发生频次: 4）\n\n#### 关键发现\n从分析的数据中，可以得出以下异常和瓶颈：\n\n- **延迟瓶颈**\n  - ProductCatalogService之间的 \"GetProduct\" 方法在多个调用链中显示显著的延迟倍数 (>2.0)\n\n- **错误传播路径**\n  - 错误 \"Region is unavailable\" 在与ProductCatalogService相关的多个调用链中被发现并传播。\n\n### 异常事件概括\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"region_unavailable\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著延迟以及区域不可用错误(Region unavailable)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常调用链中的延迟倍数达到3.44+和错误码Error 9005在多处传播。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"多次尝试与ProductCatalogService的交互出现显著延迟，发生错误传播\",\n      \"evidence\": \"对于GetProduct方法，从Frontend -> ProductCatalogService链路的延迟超过3倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n在此分析中，所有影响因素均基于调用链相关数据，错误状态码和延迟特性。上述分析结果显示了特定组件中显著的延迟瓶颈，以及错误传播引发的系统故障。", "log_analysis_findings": "已成功获取日志数据。以下是初步分析结果：\n\n### 日志分析\n在2025年06月18日19:10:04至19:29:04期间的日志显示，各个服务和节点存在许多关于区域不可用（`Region is unavailable`）的错误。这是一个可能的区域故障引发的错误模式。\n\n#### 关键日志：\n1. **productcatalogservice**:\n   - `failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`\n   - 服务节点：aiops-k8s-01, aiops-k8s-06\n\n2. **frontend**:\n   - `failed to get product recommendations: failed to get recommended product info`\n   - `could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`\n   - 服务节点：aiops-k8s-08, aiops-k8s-04, aiops-k8s-01\n\n这些错误共同指向一个可能的根因，即数据库或存储区域的不可用性影响了多个服务的正常运行。这导致产品信息查询及推荐功能无法正常使用。\n\n### 检测到的错误关键词\n- `Region is unavailable`\n- `rpc error`\n- `Error 9005 (HY000)`\n\n### 假设\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"Error 9005 (HY000)\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Region is unavailable affecting product queries\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Region is unavailable leading to rpc errors in retrieving product info\",\n      \"evidence\": \"could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n通过以上分析，我们首先关注区域服务的可用性配置，以排除由于区域不可用而导致的服务中断。接下来，还需调查具体存储或数据库服务的健康状态。"}
