出现次数:68\naiops-k8s-05,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-2,checkoutservice-2,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:4\naiops-k8s-08,productcatalogservice,checkoutservice-2,productcatalogservice-0,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-01,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"1YMWWN1N4O\"\"\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-01,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"9SIQT8TOJO\"\"\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-01,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"OLJCESPC7Z\"\"\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-05,checkoutservice,frontend-0,checkoutservice-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"OLJCESPC7Z\"\"\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-01,productcatalogservice,checkoutservice-2,productcatalogservice-2,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"OLJCESPC7Z\"\"\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-05,checkoutservice,frontend-1,checkoutservice-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"1YMWWN1N4O\"\"\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-06,productcatalogservice,checkoutservice-2,productcatalogservice-1,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-05,checkoutservice,frontend-1,checkoutservice-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"9SIQT8TOJO\"\"\",出现次数:1\n", "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-18T19:10:04Z to 2025-06-18T19:29:04Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-18 19:10:04+00:00 to 2025-06-18 19:29:04+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "metric_analysis_findings": "根据 `metric_analysis_tool` 返回的数据，以下是对当前假设的验证结果：\n\n### 验证结果\n- **异常指标**:\n  - `duration_99th` (TiDB): 从 0.01 秒升至 64.88 秒，`change_ratio`: 1.9994\n  - `failed_query_ops` (TiDB): 从 0.0 上升至 43.26，`change_ratio`: 2.0\n  - `store_unhealth_count` (TiDB-PD): 出现异常值 1.0，`change_ratio`: 2.0\n  - `rrt` (ProductCatalogService): 中位数延迟从 1322.24 毫秒增至 1048.77 毫秒, P99 从 1686.96 毫秒增至 20157109.25 毫秒，`change_ratio`: 1.9997\n\n这些指标都指出 TiDB 存储层在故障期间处理请求时遇到了显著问题，支持了与初始假设有关的 \"region_unavailable\" 错误。特别是与 `ProductCatalogService` 的响应时间和错误率急剧变化相符。\n\n### 结论\n基于以上数据支持我们之前的假设，即 `ProductCatalogService` 依赖的 `TiDB` 存储层可能是故障的根因。出现的显著性指标均指向存储的可用性和性能问题。\n\n```json\n{\n    \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n    \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"duration_99th\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"store_unhealth_count\", \"rrt\"],\n    \"hypotheses\": [\n        {\n            \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n            \"reason\": \"TiDB storage layer performance issues indicated by `duration_99th` and `failed_query_ops`.\",\n            \"evidence\": \"duration_99th increased from 0.01 to 64.88, and failed_query_ops increased from 0 to 43.26.\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n            \"reason\": \"Downstream service `ProductCatalogService` impacted by TiDB storage issues, observed in `rrt` increase.\",\n            \"evidence\": \"response time `rrt` median changed from 1322.24ms to 1048.77ms, P99 reached 20157109.25ms.\"\n        }\n    ]\n}\n```\n\n此数据支持对 TiDB 可能存在的存储层问题的初始假设，并建议进一步调查其在故障期间的性能表现。", "log_analysis_findings": "### Log 分析结果\n\n#### 识别错误模式\n从日志中提取到以下关键错误关键词：\n- `region_unavailable`\n- `rpc error`\n- `Error 9005 (HY000)`\n\n#### 区分报错者与嫌疑人\n- 多个 `frontend` 服务抱怨无法检索产品、无法获取推荐信息，出现较高的 `Region is unavailable` 错误码，指向数据库可能有问题。\n- `productcatalogservice` 也出现了 `Region is unavailable` 错误，特别是涉及查询产品 ID 的失败。\n\n#### 寻找公共嫌疑人\n- **TiDB**：多个服务（`productcatalogservice` 和 `frontend`）抱怨关于 `Region is unavailable` 的错误，表明数据库层面的可用性问题。\n- **productcatalogservice**：与前端服务的交互期间，出现了多次关于产品查询失败的记录，进一步佐证存储层的问题。\n\n### ⚠️ 特殊故障模式未识别\n没有识别出 DNS 故障或端口配置错误的特征。\n\n### 分析结论\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"region_unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"Error 9005 (HY000)\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple 'Region is unavailable' errors affecting both 'frontend' and 'productcatalogservice', indicating storage layer issues in TiDB.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Logs showing 'Region is unavailable' errors reported by 'productcatalogservice' and propagated through 'frontend'.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 总结\n日志中的错误模式支持存储层，也就是 TiDB 作为故障的根因。多个服务抱怨相同类型的错误，意见集中于 TiDB 层发生了区域不可用问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "通过分析调用链数据，我们提取了一些有助于验证假设的信息。\n\n### 调用链数据关键发现\n- **延迟显著增加:**\n  - `frontend->productcatalogservice`:\n    - 平均异常耗时: 39秒（显著延迟，正常为约11秒，延迟倍数 > 3.5）。\n  - `productcatalogservice->TiDB`:\n    - 平均异常耗时: 39秒（显著延迟，正常为约9秒，延迟倍数 > 4.3）。\n\n- **错误状态码传播:**\n  - `frontend->productcatalogservice->TiDB`链路的请求，主要错误为 `Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`，该错误多次出现并集中于 TiDB 下游调用。\n\n- **异常频率:**\n  - 在故障期间，`productcatalogservice`和调用其存储层 (TiDB) 的操作频次相对较高，表明存储服务可能由于区域不可用而延缓或拒绝了处理。\n\n- **错误传播路径的确认:**\n  - 下游异常集中在 `TiDB`。\n  - `frontend` 和 `productcatalogservice` 的异常可追溯至 `TiDB`层。\n\n### 根因假设验证\n根据调用链数据来看，该假设符合以下观察:\n1. **直接延迟:**\n   - TiDB的高延迟直接导致「ProductCatalogService」延迟累积。\n   - 前端服务 (`frontend`) 作为上游服务的受害者，其响应显著滞后，是由于下游依赖问题而受到影响。\n\n2. **错误模式:**\n   - `Region is unavailable` 作为核心错误，与 TiDB 的存储层直接关联，表明 TiDB可能确实存在区域响应问题。\n\n### 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"timeout\", \"productcatalogservice->TiDB\", \"frontend->productcatalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB\",\n      \"reason\": \"Region is unavailable错误持续出现且与显著延迟对应，下游存储层被识别为异常传播的起点。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟倍数超过4.3倍，显著错误传播（9005 HY000），调用链起点集中在TiDB。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
